{"tid":2093751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"七旬婦獲求婚墮騙局失近600萬","createTime":"2020-07-04T05:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T12:06:57.000Z","uid":252078,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8d0ae6310e1a79ff85bf03027052bc596c5800","tid":2093751,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:23:02.000Z","msg":"新蒲崗采頤花園一名<span style=\"color: red;\">70歲</span>婦人誤墮騙局，慘失近600萬元，警方拘捕一名同黨，但主要的感情騙子仍然在逃。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙警區刑事總督察莫子威交代案情稱，去年6月一名住在&lrm;新蒲崗采頤花園的70歲老婦，接到一個推廣電話，對方推介低息貸款優惠，女事主拒絕，但對方死心不息，繼續以花言巧語推介另一個建築工程的投資計劃，聲稱投資300萬元可有2萬元回報。老婦深信不疑，向財務公司借貸150萬，交予對方用作投資。至9月份，對方指有回報，將12萬元交給老婦，疑老婦感到可靠，兩人其後更發展成情侶。<br />\n<br />\n不過，狐狸終於露出尾巴，由去年10月至今年1月，騙徒6次上門向老婦苛索金錢，每次以不同藉口，包括結婚及官司纏身等等。老婦無奈變賣家產滿足「愛郎」需要，共計損失590萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n莫子威續稱，騙案非常狡猾，從未與老婦合照，雙方交收全部用現金，不留痕迹，行事非常小心。他更帶備戒指登門求婚，令老婦不能自拔。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【舊瓶新酒】七旬婦獲求婚墮騙局失近600萬 感情騙子在逃同黨被捕 <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200704&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=61128978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200704%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D61128978&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2ILc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=9b6d4492\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200704%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D61128978&h=dbebcce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200704&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=61128978</a>"},{"pid":"4d77a47744a56df70969542d7f7e88f301ab4e21","tid":2093751,"uid":4574,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:25:15.000Z","msg":"少女唔鋤愛阿婆"},{"pid":"db622d98cce6a3abc7047a220c1584fa9c4e296b","tid":2093751,"uid":324041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"居然對又老又殘嘅阿婆發動愛情攻勢，令阿婆欲仙欲死難以自拔，呢d騙徒真係冇陰功呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab98c24a8f547a2e8cbd0b12a41ed693a8057e0","tid":2093751,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f42ec97e4da465d6ea13bdd82b54e2214641263","tid":2093751,"uid":224533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"好想知犯人係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249f6cb36a8146c6fa98c202ccb80586b0a808ee","tid":2093751,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續以花言巧語推介另一個建築工程的投資計劃，聲稱投資300萬元可有2萬元回報。 </blockquote><br />\n投資300萬先得2萬回報都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca575ed6c0a7079a73851e9d019dcbd2685a0d5a","tid":2093751,"uid":89283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"70歲人都唔化"},{"pid":"c183375b2bbf5be1a137728cde2c90be4b9d1c0a","tid":2093751,"uid":155895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"有冇做愛？"},{"pid":"e6b3add103fca836f47e1538646e26504f8cbe72","tid":2093751,"uid":92479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"唔係舊酒新瓶？"},{"pid":"fcac2fc824cdd691ed17859c1c41b5db7a3d5137","tid":2093751,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"都聞到棺材香仲搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3061a49c6bbf20c3b1d7220fc66acb14c3082975","tid":2093751,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c183375b2bbf5be1a137728cde2c90be4b9d1c0a","tid":2093751,"uid":155895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"有冇做愛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫能人